# Algorithmic Art Skill

Generate algorithmic and generative art using p5.js.

## Usage

Use p5.js to create visual art through code.

## Examples

```javascript
function setup() {
  createCanvas(400, 400);
}

function draw() {
  background(220);
  ellipse(mouseX, mouseY, 50, 50);
}
```
